text: To the Orange Bowl Gators before another Super Orange Bowl Victory... I want to thank the Gators for the best, the loudest and greatest ovation I’ve ever received in my life. Gator Nation you are the BEST! - Coach S.S.
Stop by the Gator Nation Vacation Cruise booth at Fan Fest before the FSU game today! I will be signing autographs and taking pictures between 5:30 pm - 6:30 pm.
